          </div>
          <div class="details-text">
            <p>Our AI chat support widget integrates with Salesforce, Zendesk, and Shopify to deliver fast, context-aware assistance right where your teams work. With Salesforce, the AI can reference customer records or case history to provide personalized replies or update CRM data. In Zendesk, it can create and manage tickets or pull from your help center to answer common questions. For Shopify stores, it can instantly check order status, manage returns, and answer product inquiries without human intervention.</p>
            
            <p>These integrations help streamline workflows, reduce response times, and ensure efficient customer support. If your business uses other tools—like HubSpot, Freshdesk, WooCommerce, or internal systems—we can build custom integrations to meet your needs and keep your support ecosystem connected.</p>
            
